episodes.title: Nithyananda Cult Follow-Up: Inside the World of Religious Cults & My Ongoing Journey
episodes.description: I was part of the Nithyananda Cult for 2 years in 2018-2019, my experience and why i believe cults are dangerous. Along with my other experiences with religious cult like mentality.

episodes.title: Nithyananda cult- quick overview of my experience and why I left
episodes.description: This is a quick version of my experience of following Nithyananda for 1.5 years after attending a 3 week yoga/ meditation program called inner awakening. Becoming a devotee for 1 year before deciding to move there for 5 years to join a program called Paramashivoham. Luckily only staying for 5 weeks before the universe brought me back home. Thank God.
